---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SKILLS, FAVORITE_GENRES } from "../consts";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About William Lunsford">
  <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>
  <p>
    Self-taught game developer since 2022, focused on gameplay programming in Unreal Engine with C++.
    I prefer and specialize in VR game development — building for and around how people actually
    move and interact in a headset, not just porting flat-screen design onto it. I develop and test
    on a Meta Quest 3.
  </p>
  <p>
    Outside of VR-specific work, I'm generally building toward the kinds of games I play the most:
    MMORPGs, RTS, and adventure/action titles. That mix shows up in what I tend to build —
    systems-heavy gameplay, persistent worlds, and strategic depth over quick arcade loops.
  </p>

  <h2>Favorite Genres</h2>
  <p>
    {FAVORITE_GENRES.map((g) => <span class="tag">{g}</span>)}
  </p>

  <h2>Skills &amp; Tools</h2>
  <ul>
    {SKILLS.map((group) => (
      <li>{group.category}: {group.items.join(", ")}</li>
    ))}
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
